metadata.name: FiSH n BLeU
metadata.description:
FIsH n BLeU is an experimental tribute to @0xTjo's legendary artwork BLeU.

Underwater shots are probably the best blend for this blue patters. The original shot of this Nemo/Clownfish (blackfinned anemonefish) was taken while diving in Maldives. 

Edition Size: 1/1 NFT

Artists: Shinto | FloodedCamera ([@5hint0](https://twitter.com/5hint0)) x tjo ([@0xTjo](https://twitter.com/0xTjo))

Location : Guraidhoo, Maldives

License: CC0 | Free to use for any purpose. Permission granted by both the artists.
